name: David Ramirez
text: I liked this better than Interstellar. Less impressive visuals, but the plot was cleaner and the sf-ness of it was better quality.    It felt like a high budget Outer Limits episode, I guess.    We also watched John Wick 2. Amusing, also there was a bit of a Bruce Lee homage.
